      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L power plant, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been precision-serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential, providing tactile feedback and mechanical grip. The chassis integrity is superlative, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry refreshed with high-durometer OEM bushings. The exterior retains its factory luster with no discernible paint defects, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A turn-key example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
